About this item

    This fits your .
  • Make sure this fits by entering your model number.
  • Improved Tip & Ultra High Precision: JAMJAKE iPad Pencil has improved precision sensitivity and abrasion resistance, allowing you to draw natural notes and drawings without losing a single line or detail. Smooth tip reduces friction with your device and won't scratch your screen
  • Compatible with Magnetic Suction & False Function: JAMJKE iPad Pro Stylus with magnetic suction function, convenient to store and carry on business trips, meetings, etc. It also has a palm rejection, so you can freely place your hands like they are drawn on paper. Note: Compatible devices with magnetic adsorption: iPad Pro 12.9"(3rd / 4th generation); iPad Pro 11"
  • [Support tilt sensing function and convenient operation]: JAMJAKE iPad stylus can detect tilt, so you can dynamically adjust the thickness of the line according to the angle of the tip, making it ideal for drawing. It can also be used without connecting via Bluetooth. No need to set up any troublesome settings, it is very easy to turn on and off by lightly tapping the top of the stylus pen. (Note: Tilt Sensing Software: SketchBook, Procreate, Paper, Noteshelf)
  • "USB-C Rechargeable & Long Time Use" The JAMJAKE Digital Pencil is a USB-C rechargeable stylus pen. 1 hour full charge will provide 10 hours of continuous use. In static state, left for 5 minutes auto off to prevent forgetting to turn off power, helping to save battery

How are ratings calculated?
